{"tid":501943,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"｛路標達人入｝究竟俾唔俾轉左嫁/有圖","createTime":"2017-12-17T11:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T11:48:28.000Z","uid":19923,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"370b9b24214c1ba4d9be0a0b3bf3be9302986fa7","tid":501943,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:30:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/191911_233b2c630641f8359a380e21f815b736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F191911_233b2c630641f8359a380e21f815b736.jpg&h=8117d26d&s={SIZE}\" />小弟新界車多，話說出到尖沙咀呢個位呢，明明見到地標右線可以直行同轉左，但係點解人人入廣東道都會排曬起左線？搞到我都排埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但奇就奇在排到我轉左時，明明2線都係綠燈，但係我眼尾見到右線個面既<strong>行人路燈</strong>都係綠既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁如果我起右線轉左咪抄起曬d人？<br />\n<br />\n媽啊搞到我好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a534c4670afd6b750a62e813aee11730aac8d0","tid":501943,"uid":6343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:33:46.000Z","msg":"行下咪知得唔得<br />\n錯咗印度仲深d"},{"pid":"5b8343a63b7c6f16f3d993527e9dd5cee1d269fd","tid":501943,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:35:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行下咪知得唔得<br />\n錯咗印度仲深d</blockquote><br />\n唔知啊就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問過朋友又話可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff571d648c7c7f12925ce3584a2f64